    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. It currently requires significant mechanical attention, including engine work and suspension repairs, to be safely road-worthy. The exterior shows heavy wear with noticeable rust patches, several dents, and fading paint, while the interior has significant tearing and requires a deep cleaning. This would be an ideal project for a mechanic or someone looking for a parts donor car.",
