    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition, offering dependable mechanical performance despite its visible age. The exterior shows its history with several noticeable scuffs, minor door dings, and some thinning of the clear coat on the roof and hood. Inside, the upholstery is intact but displays significant wear and some permanent staining on the carpets. While it isn't a showpiece, it has been regularly serviced and remains a solid choice for anyone needing a functional, honest daily driver.",
