    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to own an absolute masterpiece! This vehicle is in breathtaking mint condition, looking and driving exactly like it did the day it left the showroom. Every inch of this car has been meticulously preserved, from the spotless interior to the gleaming exterior finish. It is a rare find for a discerning buyer who demands nothing less than perfection!",
